text: Our favorite spot to unwind after work! With plenty of dartboards, karaoke and a great selection of drinks and food, it’s the perfect place to relax. The chicken chop spaghetti is a must-try—delicious and reasonably priced! The service is top-notch, with friendly and attentive staff who always make us feel welcome. Plus point for the atmosphere as the place is clean and cosy. Highly recommend!
Had red wine with a buddy on 8/3/24, order chicken wings & spam fries, the sambal chilli that comes along was awesome. Good service too.
Everything is perfect. From the dartboards to drinks and food. Service staff is very friendly and attentive. And there’s karaoke too. Best darts venue imho.

Didn't try the food, but the beer is reasonably priced.

The pool tables are in good condition, and quite a few good players there. The pool is free.

After writing my name and waiting for 40 mins to play pool, I had to ask the staff to help me check. She then told me the players started a game with cards and money of their own and it will take another 1.5 hours.

Waste of time this place.

Staff don't have a say in the pool table.

If you're not a regular don't bother, you'll be treated like 2nd class citizen.
